      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Uninvited Guest",
        "Client": "Fugen the Elder",
        "Description": "So a Daimyo Hermitaur found its way\r\ninto the Shrine Ruins, huh? Well, time\r\nfor a little Kamura welcome. But be\r\ncareful, I hear that shell of theirs is\r\ndarn near impossible to penetrate. \r\nNot a problem for a smart hunter\r\nlike you! Bwahaha! Now go get to it!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Daimyo Hermitaur",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "H\u00F4te ind\u00E9sirable",
        "Client": "Fugen l\u0027Ancien",
        "Description": "Un Hermitaur Daimyo est\r\nentr\u00E9 dans le Temple oubli\u00E9 :\r\nc\u0027est l\u0027heure d\u0027un petit\r\naccueil \u00E0 la Kamura. On dit\r\nque sa carapace est quasi\r\nimp\u00E9n\u00E9trable, mais c\u0027est pas\r\nun probl\u00E8me pour toi. Vas-y !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Hermitaur Daimyo",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Ospite imbucato",
        "Client": "Fugen l\u0027anziano",
        "Description": "Quindi un Daimyo Hermitaur \u00E8 arrivato\r\nfino alle Rovine sacre, eh? Bene,\r\ndiamogli il benvenuto. Fai attenzione\r\nper\u00F2, ho sentito che il loro guscio \u00E8\r\nquasi impossibile da penetrare. Non\r\nsar\u00E0 un problema per \u003CLSNR {un cacciatore} {una cacciatrice}\u003E\r\nabile come te. Buahahah! Al lavoro!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Daimyo Hermitaur",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Unerbetener Gast",
        "Client": "Fogen der \u00C4lteste",
        "Description": "Ein Daimyo Hermitaur hat also seinen\r\nWeg in die Heiligen Ruinen gefunden,\r\nhm? Nun, hei\u00DFe ihn willkommen!\r\nAber vorsichtig, sein Panzer scheint\r\nfast unm\u00F6glich zu durchbrechen\r\nzu sein. Kein Problem f\u00FCr \u003CLSNR {einen} {eine}\u003E\r\n\u003CLSNR {schlauen J\u00E4ger} {schlaue J\u00E4gerin}\u003E wie dich! Bwahaha!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Daimyo Hermitaur.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Invitado indeseado",
        "Client": "Fugen el anciano",
        "Description": "As\u00ED que un Daimyo Hermitaur ha\r\nllegado hasta el Templo olvidado, \u00BFeh?\r\nHabr\u00E1 que darle una bienvenida a lo\r\nKamura. Pero, cuidado: dicen que\r\nsu caparaz\u00F3n es casi impenetrable.\r\n\u00A1Aunque eso no ser\u00E1 problema para ti!\r\n\u00A1Buaja, ja, ja! \u00A1Ve a por ello!",
        "Target": "Caza un Daimyo Hermitaur",
